data.description: This beautiful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home with a 2 car garage is now on the market and ready for its new owners. Ideal Location in Boynton Beach. Close to shopping, highways, restaurants, beaches, hospitals and much much more.  If you don't take a look at this property soon, there's a good chance another Buyer will make an offer & you'll probably spend weeks locked in your bedroom crying over it. Schedule a showing ASAP...you'll be glad you did :)  Make this house your home today...
